# Backend Alignment Verification Report

I have verified the existing `networkgraph` backend against your **Final System Vision** and **Dataset Usage Map**. Overall, the architecture and data flow are highly aligned with the vision.

## 🟢 Layer 1 — Macro View
*   **Nodes & Edges**: The implementation in [routers/graph.py](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/backend/networkgraph/routers/graph.py) correctly builds [SubredditNode](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/backend/networkgraph/models/schemas.py#13-23), [UserNode](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/backend/networkgraph/models/schemas.py#25-36), and [GraphEdge](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/backend/networkgraph/models/schemas.py#38-55) objects using the specified CSVs.
*   **Subreddit Hover**: Uses [subreddit_intelligence_summary.csv](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/data/subreddit_intelligence_summary.csv) for metrics and [echo_chamber_scores.csv](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/data/echo_chamber_scores.csv) (optional).
*   **User Profile**: Uses [user_intelligence_summary.csv](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/data/user_intelligence_summary.csv) and [author_amplification_summary.csv](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/data/author_amplification_summary.csv).
*   **Visual Encoding**: Edges are colored by `topic_cluster` (joined from [narrative_topic_mapping.csv](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/data/narrative_topic_mapping.csv)).

