*   **Data Discrepancy**: Your vision mentions `spread_sequence` as an ordered list in [narrative_spread_chain_table.csv](file:///c:/Users/Paarth/Coding/simppl/research-engineering-intern-assignment/data/narrative_spread_chain_table.csv). 
